Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.80,0:00:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,笞应我 你会把他弄上那艘船\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Promise me you'll get him on that ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.87,0:00:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-我妈妈呢 -索伦在致远星上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}- Where's my mom? - Soren on Reach?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.57,0:00:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,谁来照顾他呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Who's gonna look after him?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.71,0:00:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,站起来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.75,0:00:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你说过还有别的生活方式\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}You said there were other ways to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.31,0:00:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,-没错 -比如说什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}- That's right. - Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.58,0:00:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你们知道我看到了什么吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}You know what I see?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.98,0:00:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我看到的是一群不好惹的陆战队员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}I see some hard-ass Marines.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.09,0:00:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我在这间屋子里没有看到失败\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}I do not see defeat in this room,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.86,0:00:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我也没有看到投降\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}and I do not see surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.39,0:00:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,是 长官\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}No, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.19,0:00:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,敌军就在门口了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}The enemy is at our gates.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.50,0:00:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,数量碾压我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Their numbers are overwhelming.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.33,0:00:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,抵挡得了一时 抵挡不了一世\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}We will not be able to hold them back forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.70,0:00:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,快跑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Run.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.90,0:00:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,就让致远星沦陷吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Just let Reach fall?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.07,0:00:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,他们知道会发生这样的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}They knew this was gonna happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.91,0:00:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,他们早就预见到这种结果 于是做了权衡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}They saw it coming, they did the math.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.71,0:00:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你是什么时候离开海军情报局的 上将\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}When did you leave ONI, Admiral?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.61,0:00:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你从没离开\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}You never left.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.25,0:00:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,指挥部撤退了 高级人员也跟着走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Command bugged out. Took high-ranking personnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.92,0:00:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,还带走了高价值资产\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Valuable assets.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.08,0:00:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,他们拿走了我们的战甲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}They took our suits.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.25,0:00:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,达尼洛在哪儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Where's Danilo?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.59,0:01:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,里兹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Riz!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.59,0:01:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,他阵亡了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}He's not coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.39,0:01:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,和我们站在一起的所有陆战队员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Any Marine who makes this stand with us...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.96,0:01:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,都难逃一死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}...will not survive the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.63,0:01:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,有火吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}- Got a light?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.10,0:01:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,雅各布 我们多拖住\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}- Jacob! - For every moment
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.94,0:01:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,敌人一刻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}that we hold the enemy at bay,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.21,0:01:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,就能有更多的无辜平民登上运输飞船逃离\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}more innocent people can escape on the transports.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.08,0:01:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,他们安全离开后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}And when they do,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.21,0:01:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,会向外讲述\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}they will go forth
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.75,0:01:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你们今天谱写的故事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}and tell the story that you write today.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.95,0:01:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你们将会被铭记\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}You will be remembered...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.76,0:01:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.39,0:01:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你们是勇敢的女性和男性\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}...as the brave women and men
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.96,0:01:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,牺牲了自己的生命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}who laid down their lives
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.46,0:01:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们的孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}so that our children
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.06,0:01:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,无需生活在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}may live without fear
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.96,0:01:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,战争怪物的阴影下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}of this monster we call war.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.75,0:01:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,约翰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}John!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.35,0:02:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,约翰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}John!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.46,0:02:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,士官长\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.10,0:02:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦纳克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Vannak!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.27,0:02:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦纳克呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Where's Vannak?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.88,0:02:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我看到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}- Reloading, right side! - I see 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.34,0:02:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不能留在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}We can't stay here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.35,0:02:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们被困住 那就完了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}We get pinned down, we're done!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.18,0:02:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.35,0:02:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我们必须撤退\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}We gotta fall back!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.95,0:02:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,退到哪儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}To where?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.06,0:02:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-走 走 -行动中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}- Go! Go! - Moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.57,0:02:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,-快点 -放开我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}- Come on! - Get off me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.62,0:02:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,-快点 -放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.53,0:02:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-我还能战斗 -走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}- I can fight! - Moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.52,0:03:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,这一切还没有结束\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}It's not over.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.06,0:03:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,看看他们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Look at them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.00,0:03:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,他们回来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}They're coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.00,0:03:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,目标视野良好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Target in the open!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.12,0:03:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你们就这点本事吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Is that all you got?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.03,0:04:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我想着我不该说话 但我还是说了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}I thought I shouldn't have said anything, but I said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.44,0:04:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,-现在我后悔说话了 -别说话了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}- Now I regret saying it. - Please stop talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.97,0:04:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,就像以前一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Just like old times.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.88,0:04:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,闭嘴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.75,0:04:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,草 啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Oh, shit! Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.68,0:04:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,是我干的 是我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}I did that. That was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.59,0:04:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这事肯定是没完没了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}I'm never gonna hear the end of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.60,0:05:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Oh, you gotta be kidding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.33,0:05:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,哈尔西 起来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Halsey, get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.34,0:05:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,约翰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}[Soren] John.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.84,0:05:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,能帮我一把吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Can I get a little help over here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.81,0:05:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,上来 我们走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Get in! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.35,0:05:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我们抓住他了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}We got him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.22,0:05:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,他们来了 快点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}They're coming! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.02,0:05:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,进来 我们快走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Get in. Get us out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.63,0:05:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦纳克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Vannak.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.96,0:05:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,别\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.00,0:05:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,里兹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Riz!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.89,0:05:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,里兹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Riz...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.66,0:06:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,别去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.46,0:06:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,快点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.37,0:06:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,里兹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Riz!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.61,0:07:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,坚持\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}- Get us out of here! - Hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.95,0:07:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,检查她的呼吸道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}- Riz. - Check her airway.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.89,0:07:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,是我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.07,0:07:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,约翰 约翰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}John! John!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.10,0:07:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,-里兹 -看着我 别睡过去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}- Riz... - Look at me. Stay with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.81,0:07:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,别睡过去 约翰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}- No, Riz... - Stay with me, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.78,0:07:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,士官长\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.58,0:07:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,醒醒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.28,0:07:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我来看着他 约翰 约翰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}I've got him. John. John?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.98,0:07:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,-约翰 醒醒 -里兹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}- John, wake up. - Riz...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.82,0:07:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,救她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Save her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.49,0:07:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该和我在一起的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}You should have stayed with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.86,0:07:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,断开连接\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Sever the connection.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.29,0:07:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要失去他了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}We're losing him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.00,0:07:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.27,0:07:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了 你能救他吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Please, will you help him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.84,0:07:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,那得看情况\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}That depends.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.94,0:07:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你愿意为我做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}What are you prepared to do for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.61,0:09:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你用这次大胜给我们的族人带来了荣耀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.38,0:09:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,这次不算胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.78,0:09:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我们只找回了一块被盗的基石
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.82,0:09:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,而且世尊者再次否定了我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.87,0:09:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,朝圣之旅的每一步都有它该走的时间和地点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.91,0:10:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经厌倦了你的天赋 这个预言
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.08,0:10:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,恶魔的死亡将是我的救赎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.09,0:10:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你却保护他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.75,0:10:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我不在乎恶魔 我是为了更高层次的使命 你也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.30,0:10:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,别跟我来这套 人类
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.68,0:10:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我提醒你一下 你还活着都是因为我大发慈悲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.40,0:10:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我活着让你受到了冒犯 那就杀了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.34,0:10:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,这个人类的东西有什么价值
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.92,0:10:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,这是个载体
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.05,0:10:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,里面有什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.05,0:10:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,知识 人类的知识
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.15,0:11:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,它能告诉我们他们把基石带去哪儿了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.44,0:11:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,也许吧 我得看了才知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.45,0:11:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,那就去看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.11,0:12:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,她不应该回去找他的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}She shouldn't have gone back for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.14,0:12:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,-她应该知道的 -你需要休息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}- She knows better than that. - You need to rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.11,0:12:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,-你的伤口还没愈合好 -她能活下来吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}- Your wound is still healing. - Is she gonna live?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.65,0:12:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,她需要手术 我这里没有工具\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}She needs surgery. I don't have the tools here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.19,0:12:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,她觉得她要证明些什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}She thought she had something to prove.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.09,0:12:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我利用了这点逼她证明自己\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}And I used that to push her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.46,0:12:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,她是因为我才回去的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}She went back because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.17,0:12:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,她回去是因为斯巴达战士\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}She went back because Spartans
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.10,0:12:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不会丢下斯巴达战士\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}don't leave Spartans behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.47,0:12:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,没有斯巴达战士被丢下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}There was no Spartan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.14,0:12:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,他已经死了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}He was already gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.94,0:13:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,她评估了情况 做出了决定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}She evaluated the conditions and made a decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.74,0:13:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,什么决定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}What decision is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.85,0:13:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,什么时候开始我们会做决定了 我们不做选择\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Since when do we decide anything? We don't choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.12,0:13:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你告诉我们该去哪里 该怎么想 该杀谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}You told us where to go and what to think, who to kill,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.85,0:13:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我们每次都照做 绝不多问\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}and we did that every time, without question.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.66,0:13:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你像士兵一样服从命令\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}You followed orders like soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.99,0:13:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,-像机器一样 -你不是机器\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}- Like machines. - You're not a machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.93,0:13:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,噢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.66,0:13:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,那么我是什么呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}What am I, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.67,0:13:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不要说人类 因为真正的人有自己的生活\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Don't say human, because real people have lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.84,0:13:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,有家人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}They have families.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.54,0:13:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,-有各种可能的未来 -你很伤心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}- Possibilities. - You're upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.38,0:13:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,-我们都是 -看看她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}- We all are. - Look at her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.88,0:13:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,看看她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Look at her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.05,0:13:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,-告诉我你看到了什么 -放手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}- Tell me what you see. - Let go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.72,0:13:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我你看到了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Tell me what you see!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.39,0:13:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,那是个女人还是把武器\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Is that a woman or a weapon?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.15,0:13:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,那是一个人吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Is there a person in there,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.66,0:13:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,还是只是你留在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}or is that just a piece of equipment
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.19,0:13:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,战场上的一件装备 扔了就扔了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}you leave on the battlefield, dump and forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.88,0:14:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,他们把我们丢在那里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}They left us down there...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.65,0:14:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,自生自灭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.85,0:14:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.69,0:14:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,没有撤离计划 没有战甲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}No evac, no armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.49,0:14:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-海军情报局知道我们肯定会死 -我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}- ONI knew we wouldn't make it. - I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.06,0:14:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,致远星上的其他队伍呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}What about the other teams on Reach?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.27,0:14:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,有动静吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Any contact?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.54,0:14:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,凯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Kai?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.91,0:14:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,一片混乱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}It was chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.21,0:14:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,这座城市沦陷了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}The city fell.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.05,0:14:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,飞船四散奔逃\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Ships scattered.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.42,0:14:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,没有办法知道有多少人逃脱了 更不用说知道谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}There's no way of telling how many escaped, let alone who--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.42,0:14:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,-多久了 -我得让你进入诱导性昏迷\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}- How long have I--? - I had to induce a coma.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.46,0:14:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,-多久了 -两天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}- How long? - Two days.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.73,0:15:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,-两天 -两天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}- Two days. - Two days?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.93,0:15:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得回去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}We gotta get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.10,0:15:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-我们得 -约翰 别说了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}- We gotta go-- - John, stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.57,0:15:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,-幸存者们 -约翰 约翰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}- The survivors-- - John, John...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.40,0:15:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,致远星的人们需要我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}People on Reach, they need me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.40,0:15:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.60,0:15:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,不 他们不需要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}No, they don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.96,0:15:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你发烧了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}You have a fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.22,0:15:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你状态不好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}You're not yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.83,0:15:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我告诉了他们会发生什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}I told them what would happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.76,0:15:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,-好了 -我告诉他们了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}- Come on. - I told them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.73,0:15:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我告诉艾克森了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}I told Ackerson.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.51,0:15:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,他们已经知道了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}They already knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.18,0:15:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,他们知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}They knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.51,0:15:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,他们还是什么也没做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}And they did nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.32,0:15:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我本可以阻止这一切的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}I could have stopped it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.99,0:16:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我 有战甲的话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}If I just... had my armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.19,0:16:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,如果她和我在一起的话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}If she was with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.76,0:16:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,致远星沦陷不是意外\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Reach wasn't an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.96,0:16:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,是计划内的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}It was a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.37,0:16:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要小心行事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}We need to be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.54,0:16:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,藏起来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Invisible.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.84,0:16:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你明白吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.21,0:16:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,所以\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}So...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.22,0:16:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,现在又是“我们”了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}it's "we" now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.52,0:16:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,一直都是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}It always has been.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.53,0:16:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你能听到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}I know you hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.73,0:16:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你能看到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}I know you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.20,0:16:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你害怕了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Are you afraid?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.80,0:16:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我召唤你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}I summon you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.87,0:16:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我以高等先知的名义召唤你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}I summon you in the name of the Hierarchs,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.91,0:16:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,众神之声\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}voices of the gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.48,0:16:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,下次 你可以直接按那个小按钮\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Next time, you can just push the little button there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.48,0:17:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,真有意思\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Fascinating.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.52,0:17:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,这是艘星盟的飞船\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}This is a Covenant ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.82,0:17:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这是狂徒尊者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}This is the command vessel
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.39,0:17:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦尔加塔奈的指挥舰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}of the esteemed Zealot, Var'Gatanai,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.22,0:17:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,他是庄严协议第一舰队的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}former Supreme Commander of the First Fleet
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.53,0:17:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,前最高指挥官\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}of Solemn Accord.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.73,0:17:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,神风烈士\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}The Arbiter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.03,0:17:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}What are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.40,0:17:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我是科塔娜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}I am Cortana,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.07,0:17:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,-最先进的人工智 -不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}- the most advanced artificial-- - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.41,0:17:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你对他来说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}What are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.51,0:17:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.78,0:17:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,士官长吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Master Chief?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.85,0:17:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.88,0:17:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我们一起工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}We work together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.92,0:17:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你对那个恶魔了解多少\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}What do you know of the demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.09,0:17:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,他记得你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}He remembers you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.63,0:17:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你还留着他的记忆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}You keep his memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.26,0:17:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,给我看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Show me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.35,0:17:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,给我看看他对光环的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.27,0:17:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,它不属于你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}It doesn't belong to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.94,0:18:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不属于你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.78,0:18:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你对我来说没用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.07,0:18:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,那我对高等先知就没用了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.91,0:18:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你我都知道没用的东西有什么下场
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.59,0:18:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,世界上有很多种监狱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.81,0:18:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你醒了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}There you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.91,0:18:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你在说梦话来着\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}You talk in your sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.98,0:18:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,他醒了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}He's back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.82,0:18:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 哥们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Hey, buddy.
