Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.93,0:25:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,-没区别 -对我来说有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}- It makes no difference. - It does to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.43,0:25:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,要把他们埋入地下 留他们在原地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}You put them in the ground and you leave them there.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.64,0:25:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不然他们会跟着你的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Or they will follow you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.47,0:26:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我捋一下哈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}So let me get this straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.47,0:26:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你给清理干净 然后那片土地就是你的了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}You gotta clean it up, but then the land is yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.81,0:26:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,-对 差不多吧 -不错哎 有什么条件吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}- Yeah, pretty much. - Nice. What's the catch?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.14,0:26:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,-没条件 -没条件吗 跟他说呀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}- No catch. - No catch? Tell him.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.91,0:26:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,-我们不能离开 -永远都不可以吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}- Well, we can't leave. - Not ever?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.41,0:26:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 但谁会想走呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}[woman] Yeah, but who'd want to, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.95,0:26:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,看看这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}I mean, look at this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.98,0:26:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我为你们高兴 很美 对吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}I'm happy for you. It's beautiful, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.15,0:26:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,-别这样了 -怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}- Stop. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.99,0:26:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你在交朋友 欣赏风景\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}You're making friends and enjoying the scenery.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.16,0:26:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在找我们的儿子 索伦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}We're looking for our son, Soren.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.36,0:26:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.13,0:26:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我们之前在致远星 这么多人 都死了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}We were on Reach. All those people. They're gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.77,0:26:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,整座城市\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}A whole city.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.04,0:26:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,整个星球\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}A whole planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.68,0:26:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,这些都不会让你触动吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Does none of that touch you?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.98,0:27:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,-当然会了 -那就表现出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}- Of course, it does. - Then act like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.61,0:27:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你想我难过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}You want me to be sad?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.12,0:27:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,害怕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.45,0:27:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,总得有人往前看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Somebody's gotta keep looking forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.52,0:27:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,每次一出天塌了的大事 你永远都不在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}When things fall apart, you're never there.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.16,0:27:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你逃离了斯巴达计划\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}You ran from the Spartan program.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.49,0:27:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,从碎石星逃出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}You ran from the Rubble.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.30,0:27:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,鲁比·安找我们的时候 就全靠我一人撑着\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}When Ruby Ann came for us, it was all on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.86,0:27:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,等下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Whoa, whoa. Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.37,0:27:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,这事你不能怪我头上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}You can't blame me for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.30,0:27:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你在 他们会来对付我们吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Would they have come for us if you'd been there?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.71,0:27:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我确实希望你伤心 希望你害怕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}And I do want you to be sad and I do want you to be scared,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.34,0:27:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我就是这种感觉 我希望你也是一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}because that's where I am and I want you with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.72,0:27:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,还有你的完美爱人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}♪ And your perfect lover ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.76,0:27:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,看起来像个十足的傻瓜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}♪ Just looks like A perfect fool ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.00,0:27:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你要逃跑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}♪ So you go running off ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.36,0:27:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,寻找一个完全陌生的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}♪ In search Of a perfect stranger ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.00,0:27:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,而孤独\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}♪ While the loneliness ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.57,0:28:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,似乎从你生活中涌出\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}♪ Seems to spring From your life ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.74,0:28:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你当时就是这个表情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}This is exactly how you looked.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.95,0:28:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我那年14岁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}I was 14.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.29,0:28:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,做完增强手术后醒过来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}I woke up after the augmentation and...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.49,0:28:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你看向我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}you looked at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.96,0:28:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你还记得当时自己说了什么吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Do you remember what you said?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.96,0:28:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,眼睛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.33,0:28:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,往上看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Look up.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.97,0:29:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,三个当中活了一个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}"One out of three."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.60,0:29:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,很多比我强的人都没能活下来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Oh, so many that were better than me didn't survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.61,0:29:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我们中枪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}We get shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.58,0:29:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,受伤\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}We get hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.98,0:29:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,站起来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}We get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.65,0:29:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,再重来一遍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}We do it all again.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.12,0:29:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我只会这样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}That's all I know how to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.15,0:29:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我把一切都教给你了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}I taught you everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.92,0:29:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,除了如何放弃\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Except how to quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.62,0:29:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是为了你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}I don't do it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.93,0:29:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,里兹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Riz...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.43,0:29:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我尽力了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}I did everything I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.37,0:29:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,但伤势太严重了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}But the damage is significant.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.84,0:29:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你没法恢复原来的状态了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}You won't be the soldier you once were.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.18,0:29:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你本来状态就不比从前\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}You were already diminished.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.15,0:29:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,所以\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}So...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.35,0:29:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你必须更加努力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}you'll have to work harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.06,0:30:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么这么大只啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Why'd you have to be so big?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.73,0:30:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,走啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.04,0:30:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,这样如何\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}How's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.08,0:30:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,是 我也是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Yeah, me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.59,0:31:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,伤害不断累积\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Damage accumulates.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.72,0:31:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,她回不去以前的状态了 但时间会帮到她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}She won't be the same as she was, but time will help.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.03,0:31:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,里兹会活下来 会再次投入战斗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Riz will live and she will fight again.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.90,0:31:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我们所有人都不复以往了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}[John] Well, none of us are what we were.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.40,0:31:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我们可有可无\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}And now we're expendable.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.94,0:31:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,致远星上发生的事并不是针对个人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}What happened on Reach wasn't personal.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.57,0:31:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至不是策略需要 是政治原因\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}It wasn't even strategic. It was political.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.21,0:31:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,是巴拉戈斯基\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}It was Parangosky.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.62,0:31:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}This...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.65,0:31:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,事关控制权\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}This was about control.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.42,0:31:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,事关由谁决定这场战争怎么打\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}About who dictates how this war is fought.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.59,0:31:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,她赢了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}She won.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.43,0:31:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你没法为整个星球哀悼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}You can't grieve an entire planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.77,0:31:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,太宏大了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}It's too big.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.27,0:31:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的思想不会让它成为现实\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Our minds won't let it be real.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.34,0:31:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,所有这此生命 这些名字\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}All those lives. All those names.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.78,0:31:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,太多了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}It's too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.68,0:32:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我要你帮我做件事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}I need you to do something for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.98,0:32:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我之前没机会埋葬别人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}I never got to bury anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.45,0:32:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,没埋葬过我的人民\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Not my people.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.52,0:32:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我的家人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Not my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.79,0:32:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不知怎么的 我需要你当所有逝者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Somehow, I need you to be everyone that's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.03,0:32:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你能做到吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Can you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.01,0:32:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,取出科塔娜的人就是巴拉戈斯基\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Parangosky's the one who took Cortana out.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.51,0:32:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么可能记得这此\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}How could you possibly have remembered that?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.15,0:32:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不清楚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.02,0:32:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,里面有个空间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}There's a space inside...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.99,0:32:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,那里曾经有个声音\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}where there used to be a voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.19,0:32:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得有人认识我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}I'm feeling that somebody knew me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.73,0:32:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,有些东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}There was something that...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.46,0:32:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,科塔娜说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Cortana said...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.20,0:32:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,就在她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}right before she...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.54,0:32:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,继续\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.80,0:32:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,什么 她说了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}What? What-- What did she say?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.97,0:33:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你是怎么选的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}How did you choose...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.64,0:33:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,什么意思\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}W-W-W-What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.81,0:33:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你是怎么选上我的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}How did you choose me?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.88,0:33:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我们创建了基因档案\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}We created the genetic profile.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.72,0:33:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,-调查过所有孩子 -不是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}- We surveyed all the children-- - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.99,0:33:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么选我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.56,0:33:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,-我不明白 -你明白的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}-  I don't understand. - Yes, you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.90,0:33:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,说实话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Tell the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.87,0:33:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,就这一次\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Just once.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.42,0:33:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,还没聊完呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}We're not done here.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.79,0:33:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,后退\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.60,0:34:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,再靠近一步 我就拉你们陪葬了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Come closer, I will dig another hole!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.97,0:34:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,-你干什么呢 -嘿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}- What are you doing? - Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.54,0:34:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,这帮疯子要带走他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}This crazy's trying to take him!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.47,0:34:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能把他埋入地下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}You can't put him in the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.57,0:34:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我不同意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}I beg to differ!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.78,0:34:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,把这尸体烧了 让他去找自己的路\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Burn this body. Let him find his way.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.78,0:34:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 嘿嘿嘿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Whoa. Hey, hey, hey, hey, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.78,0:34:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.98,0:34:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,-别碰他 -住手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}- Get your hands off him! - Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.26,0:34:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,士官长\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Chief?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.93,0:34:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是死亡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}This isn't death.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.90,0:34:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,这是失去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}This is loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.24,0:34:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,是有区别的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}There's a difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.78,0:34:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,火葬吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Put him in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.50,0:35:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}[man] All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.81,0:35:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,-索伦 -在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}- Soren. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.55,0:36:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,-什么事 -晚上好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}- What do you want? - Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.06,0:36:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你这叫非法闯入\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}You're trespassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.49,0:36:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,-容我解释 -我们是来找儿子的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}- Allow me to explain. - We're here for our son.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.83,0:36:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,-什么 -我们的儿子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}- Your what? - Our son.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.16,0:36:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,凯斯勒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Kessler.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.40,0:36:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,很听话的小男孩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Nice boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.93,0:36:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,-差不多这么高 -他是我们的孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}- Like, yay, high-- - The kid is ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.10,0:36:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,鬼扯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}- The hell he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.67,0:36:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,冷静一点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Now... let's calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.54,0:36:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,去别地儿冷静去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}You can calm down somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.74,0:36:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,这个家很好 他喜欢这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}This is a good home and he likes it here,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.54,0:36:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,要是我把他交给了两个陌生人 那我是真该死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}and I'll be damned if I'm giving him up to a couple of strangers.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.41,0:36:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不是陌生人 我们是他的父母\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}We're not strangers. We're his parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.75,0:36:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,就算是真的 你们也不会是合格的父母\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Even if that were true, some parents you'd be.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.35,0:36:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,他来到这里时 饿得半死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}He was half starved when he got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.05,0:36:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,看上去还挨了不少揍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Looked like he'd been slapped around a little too.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.62,0:36:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,-你说什么 -对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}- What did you say? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.62,0:36:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我想现在知道罪魁祸首是谁了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}I guess we know who's responsible for that now.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.63,0:36:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,草 凯斯勒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Fuck you! Kessler!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.60,0:36:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,凯斯勒 快出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Kessler, come out here right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.23,0:36:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,凯斯勒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Kessler!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.10,0:36:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,他就在这里 她们带走了他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}They have him. They took him.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.44,0:36:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的 不会有事的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}It's okay. It's gonna be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.91,0:36:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,-冷静 -我们要怎么办\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}- Calm down. - What are we gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.08,0:36:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我在呢 我能处理好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}I'm here. I can handle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.95,0:37:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,-不就是场谈判嘛 -这关系到我们的儿子啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}- It's a negotiation. - It's our son.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.45,0:37:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,相信我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.12,0:37:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我马上回来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.11,0:37:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 你们看上去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Well, you all seem...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.78,0:37:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,准备充足\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.18,0:37:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你永远不知道世界什么时候会崩塌\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}You never know when the world's gonna fall apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.18,0:37:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,确实\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.42,0:37:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,这茶真不错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}This is some really good tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.49,0:37:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你让我们给你五分钟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}You said to give you five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.59,0:37:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,已经过了两分钟了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}We already gave you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.83,0:37:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我小时候生活的地方和这里很像\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}I grew up in a place just like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.30,0:37:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,什么意思\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.97,0:37:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,意思是 我知道勉强维生是什么感觉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}It means I know what it is to scratch out a life.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.17,0:37:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,大地产出的粮食总是达不到预期\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}The ground never gives you what it promised.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.31,0:38:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,吃的食物永远不够\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}There's never quite enough to go around.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.64,0:38:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我们凑合能过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}We get by.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.51,0:38:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我能搞来东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}I'm the kind of guy that can get things.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.45,0:38:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,能给予你们补偿的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}The kind of things that can compensate.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.99,0:38:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道多一双手意味着什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}I know what an extra pair of hands can mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.88,0:38:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的儿子不卖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Our boy isn't for sale.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.39,0:38:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,实话和你们说吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}I'm gonna be honest with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.50,0:39:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,这里和我长大的地方完全不一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}This is nothing like where I grew up.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.40,0:39:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我出生在地狱里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}I was born in hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.34,0:39:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,在拳打脚踢下长大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Raised in violence.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.24,0:39:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,没有家人 没有家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Being without a family, without a home...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.25,0:39:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,没有食物 没有人保护我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}without food, without protection.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.72,0:39:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,凯斯勒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Kessler!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.09,0:39:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,宝贝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Baby?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.26,0:39:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我发现 我能挺过这一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}I realized I can survive all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.53,0:39:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,但是孤独\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}But the loneliness...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.57,0:39:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,要说什么能要我命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}If anything was gonna kill me...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.61,0:39:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是孤独\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}it would be that.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.81,0:39:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,真的是我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}It's really me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.11,0:39:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我当父亲了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}So now I'm a father.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.05,0:39:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我生活在恐惧里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}And I live in fear...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.95,0:39:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.45,0:39:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,不过我的儿子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}...that my boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.89,0:39:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,永远体会不到那种感觉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}will never know that feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.29,0:40:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,永远体会不到缺少爱是什么感觉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}That absence of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.23,0:40:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,感恩是你们收留了他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}I am grateful that you're the ones that took him in,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.34,0:40:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我知道 他迟早能在这里找到爱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}because I know in time, he'd find love here.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.98,0:40:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,但他是我的儿子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}But he's my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.27,0:40:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你从哪弄来的这个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Where did you get this?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.17,0:40:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,一个男孩给我的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}A boy gave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.01,0:40:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,在运输飞船上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}On the transport.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.54,0:40:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,用来保护自己的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}For protection.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.88,0:40:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,他 他发现我害怕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}He-- He saw that I was scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.78,0:40:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,他在哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.02,0:41:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,被他们带走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}They took him away.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.07,0:41:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,她们愿意让我们见凯斯勒了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}They're gonna let us see Kessler.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.90,0:41:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,那是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Is that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.24,0:41:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.67,0:41:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不是凯斯勒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}It's not Kessler.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.77,0:41:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,致远星不仅是一个地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Reach was more than a place.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.11,0:41:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,更是一个象征\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}It was a symbol.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.78,0:41:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,是人类精神的丰碑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}It was a monument to the human spirit...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.58,0:42:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,纪念着牺牲了一切保卫这里的人们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}and to those who sacrificed everything to defend it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.22,0:42:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,比如雅各布·凯斯上将\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Those like Admiral Jacob Keyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.79,0:42:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,以及这位斯巴达战士 瓦纳克·阿马迪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}And this Spartan, Vannak Amadi.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.10,0:42:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,他在致敬星上出生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}He was born on Tribute.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.77,0:42:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我认识他时他才六岁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}I met him when he was six.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.57,0:42:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我能看得出来 他很有荣誉感\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}I could see he had honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.31,0:42:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,他生活在大家族里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}He had a large family.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.94,0:42:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,他尽忠效劳他的家人会为他骄傲的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}They would be proud of his service.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.75,0:42:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,他的家人在他六岁时就埋葬了他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}His family buried him when he was six.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.59,0:42:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,他们从来不了解他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}They never knew him.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.30,0:42:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,但我了解\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}But I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.34,0:43:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,他的名字是瓦纳克-134\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}His name was Vannak-134.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.01,0:43:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,他是个斯巴达战士\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}He was a Spartan.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.32,0:43:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,是我们的兄弟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}He was our brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.98,0:43:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,他也是自己认识的唯一的亲人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}And the only family that he ever knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.16,0:43:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,他 他这一生并不平凡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}This... This was not an ordinary man.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.13,0:43:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,他做过的一切 付出的一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Everything that he was, everything that he gave...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.04,0:43:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,永垂不朽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}it never dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.86,0:43:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你的战斗没有结束\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Your fight is not done.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.46,0:43:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我会成为你的武器\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}I will be your weapon now.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.36,0:44:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我会找到害死你的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}I will find the ones who caused your death,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.03,0:44:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,要了他们的命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}and I will end them.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.46,0:45:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得你能接近巴拉戈斯基\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}You think you can get to Parangosky?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.20,0:45:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,接近艾克森吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}To Ackerson?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.43,0:45:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你连他们在哪里都不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}You don't even know where they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.94,0:45:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我会找到他们的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}I'll find them.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.27,0:45:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你只会害死你自己\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}You're gonna get yourself killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.11,0:45:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有选择你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}I didn't choose you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.22,0:45:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我找到了你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}I found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.12,0:45:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不管是什么东西打造了光环\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Whatever built the Halo,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.65,0:45:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不管是什么东西留下了那些制品\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}whatever left those artifacts behind,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.42,0:45:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,它们也在你的内心留下了点什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}left something in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.29,0:45:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你逃避不了的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}You can't run from this.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.63,0:45:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,这是你一辈子的召唤\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}This has been calling to you your whole life.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.47,0:45:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,这是你注定要完成的使命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}This is what you're meant to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.40,0:45:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在只有一件事情要做 那就是找到巴拉戈斯基和艾克森\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}The only thing I have to do is find Parangosky, Ackerson.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.34,0:45:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,约翰 你能带我们去光环\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}John, you can take us to the Halo.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.74,0:45:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我们种族能不能活下来 就看光环能教会我们什么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}The survival of our species depends on what it can teach us.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.08,0:46:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你自己去找海军情报局报仇 那就是让我们所有人陪你冒险\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}If you go after ONI yourself, you put all of that at risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.15,0:46:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,他们不会给你留生路的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}They can't let you live.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.13,0:46:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经死了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}I'm already dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.51,0:46:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,加入我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Join us.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.01,0:46:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.55,0:46:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思 你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Sorry, did...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.19,0:46:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你刚才和我说了什么吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Did you say something to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.99,0:46:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我代表星球说话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}I speak for the planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.23,0:46:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Oh, you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.90,0:46:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我代表所有星球说话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}I speak for all the planets.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.80,0:46:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.51,0:46:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,人都去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Where is...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.74,0:46:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我代表牧歌星说话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}I speak for Madrigal.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.65,0:47:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你说什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.15,0:47:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我痛苦地呐喊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}[woman] I cry out in pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.55,0:47:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我的孩子灰飞烟灭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}My children are ash.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.59,0:47:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我的皮肤破裂 我的心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}My skin is broken. My heart--
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.52,0:47:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,-你是谁啊 -你是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}- Who the hell are you? - Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.70,0:47:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,谁也不是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}No one.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.37,0:47:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你是韩关\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}You're Kwan Ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.57,0:47:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,韩氏一族最后一人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Last of the Has.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.21,0:47:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}How...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.04,0:47:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}How do you...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.41,0:47:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,-你是谁 -你背叛了我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}- Who are you? - You turned your back on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.95,0:47:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,-你忘记了自己的姓名 -别过来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}- You forgot your name. - Get away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.42,0:47:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,靠近了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}It's close now.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.29,0:47:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,-怪物 -你别过来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}- The monster. - Stay where you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.42,0:47:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,帮助我 找到我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Help me. Find me.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.59,0:47:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,拯救我 解救我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Deliver me. Save me.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.39,0:47:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不要否认你的使命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Do not deny your purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.93,0:47:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-不要抛弃你的姓名 -别说了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}- Do not forsake your name. - Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.76,0:47:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,守护者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Protector.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.90,0:48:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你说什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}What did you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.34,0:48:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你做了什么 我们怎么在博爱城
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.91,0:48:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的舰队被召回了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.03,0:48:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不我们有任务 要去找回
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.82,0:48:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,任务失败了 接受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.59,0:48:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道他们会怎么对我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.42,0:48:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么对我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.04,0:49:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,只能希望 他们会接受这个信物
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.42,0:49:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,作为我失败的补偿
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.30,0:49:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不要这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.05,0:49:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,高等先知已经下令了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.31,0:49:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,高等先知是骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.31,0:49:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你再辱骂一句 我就撕碎你
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.81,0:49:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,先知满嘴谎言
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.23,0:49:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,他们根本没想着开启朝圣之旅
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.49,0:49:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,他们没有能力这么做 他们非天选之人
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.70,0:49:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,他们心知肚明 这是我们的命运 我看见了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.08,0:49:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你能带领我们前往圣迹环带
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.00,0:49:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你拍的马屁既残忍又空洞
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.42,0:49:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,这些先知让你为此感到羞愧 因为他们惧怕你
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.46,0:49:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,他们看到了你的伟大和你纯粹的信念
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.96,0:49:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,他们因自己的虚伪而窒息
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.88,0:50:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.31,0:50:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不是我 是你
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.68,0:50:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,这是你的命运 你只要接受就好
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.40,0:50:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我要怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.40,0:50:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,相信 你要相信 相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.86,0:50:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我是世尊者
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.82,0:50:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,他们会派出一整支舰队来追捕我们
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.04,0:50:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,他们会失败的
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.17,0:51:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,一切早已命中注定
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.08,0:52:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,需要帮忙吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.48,0:52:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,有手套吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Gloves?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.55,0:52:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,就在那边\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Right over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.43,0:52:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,是你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Oh, it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.40,0:52:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你这样我没认出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}I didn't recognize you with your...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.70,0:52:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,有带刺铁丝网吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Do you have any barbed wire?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.57,0:53:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,那个和你一起的家伙呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Where's that, uh, fella that was with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.94,0:53:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,他想来的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}He wanted to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.61,0:53:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,但我觉得这样不太慎重\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}But I didn't think that would be prudent.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.45,0:53:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,慎重\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Prudent?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.58,0:53:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,他有点情绪化\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}He can be a bit emotional.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.72,0:53:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,这种情况我看得更明白\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Whereas I see this kind of situation a bit more clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.63,0:53:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,-我没明白 -你肯定明白\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}- I don't think I understand. - Of course you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.03,0:53:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你以前有过妈妈 对吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}You had a mother, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.87,0:53:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-对 -没有人应该挡在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}- Yeah. - No one should come
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.77,0:53:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈和孩子之间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}between a mother and her child.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.77,0:53:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,这个纽带很强大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}It's a powerful bond.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.81,0:53:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,天生的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Instinctive.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.47,0:53:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我们这里来过很多孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}You know, we got a lot of kids coming through here--
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.28,0:53:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,几天前\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}The other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.29,0:53:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我在空气里闻到了一丝气味 让我回到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}I caught a scent in the air, that took me back
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.62,0:53:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我第一次给凯斯勒剪头发的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}to the first time I cut Kessler's hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.46,0:53:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,他那时还那么小\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}He was so little.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.93,0:53:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,女士 我就是个开店的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Look, lady, I-- I'm just a businessman.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.10,0:54:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,他扭来扭去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}He was squirming.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.93,0:54:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我担心会划伤他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}I was nervous that I would hurt him.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.94,0:54:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,那个时候我就知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}And that's when I knew...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.67,0:54:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,如果谁伤害了他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}that if anyone ever caused him pain,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.18,0:54:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不知道自己会做出什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}there's no telling what I would do.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.75,0:54:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不惜一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}There would be no limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.69,0:54:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道我的意思吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}You know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:37.00,0:54:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,他说了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Did he talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.50,0:54:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,说了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.47,0:54:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,他说了凯斯勒是被谁带走的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Did he say who took Kessler?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.34,0:54:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,联合国太空指挥部\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}The UNSC.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.16,0:55:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,十分钟后出发\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}We're wheels up in ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.86,0:55:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,里兹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Riz...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.37,0:55:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,-收拾一下 -我做不到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}- get your stuff-- - I'm not gonna make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.74,0:55:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你说什么呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.87,0:55:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,-你没事的 -我要留在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}- You're gonna be fine. - I'm gonna stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.91,0:55:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,焦中注意力打仗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Get your head in the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.58,0:55:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我的战争结束了 长官\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}My fight's over, Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.99,0:55:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦纳克说结束时才结束\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}It's over when Vannak says it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.06,0:55:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,-凯说 -士官长\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}- When Kai says-- - Chief--
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.23,0:55:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,赢了才算结束\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}It's over when we win!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.23,0:55:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,站起来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}On your feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.07,0:55:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我命令你 斯巴达战士\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}I gave you an order, Spartan.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.34,0:55:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,站起来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Stand up.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.22,0:56:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我们失去了致远星\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}We lost Reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.09,0:56:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我们失去了瓦纳克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}We lost Vannak...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.23,0:56:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-凯 -我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}- Kai... - I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.56,0:56:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,那你打算怎么做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}Then what are you gonna do about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.53,0:56:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我要活下去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}I'm going to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.74,0:56:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你没资格说不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}You don't get to say no to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.07,0:56:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我们欠他们的 里兹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}We owe them, Riz.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.48,0:56:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我们失去了他们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}We lost them.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.15,0:56:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,-我失去了他们 -只是痛苦而已\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}- I lost them. - It's just pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.58,0:56:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你能做的只有带着痛苦前行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}All you can do is carry it.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.79,0:56:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,它很沉重\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}But it's heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.95,0:56:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,但你越不愿面对 越逃避\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}And the more you deny it, the more you run from it,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.82,0:56:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,它就会变得越沉重\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}the heavier it gets.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.89,0:56:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你不和痛苦和解 你会被压垮的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}If you don't make peace with it, it will crush you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.80,0:56:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会让痛苦压垮我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}I won't let it crush me.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.40,0:56:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我只有你了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}You're all I have left.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.94,0:57:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.67,0:57:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,她不来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}She's not coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.18,0:57:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,那\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}So...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.01,0:57:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在谁也不是了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}you're no one now.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.14,0:59:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,全体都有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H62a8eb&}[Marine] Attention on deck!

